# agent-stack

AI agent configuration for agentic coding in Cursor. Single stack: Supabase, Better Auth, Hono, tRPC, React, TanStack Router + Query, Shadcn.

Shared across projects via git submodule. Improve a prompt once — every project gets it.

---

## What's Inside

```
agent-stack/
├── agents/
│   ├── discovery/                    # Phase 0 — requirements, UI spec, test strategy
│   │   ├── requirements-agent.md     # Dialog → 00-requirements.md
│   │   ├── ux-designer-agent.md      # Dialog → 01-ui-spec.md (conditional)
│   │   └── test-strategist-agent.md  # → 02-test-spec.md
│   ├── planning/                     # Phase 1 — plan and tickets
│   │   ├── orchestrator-agent.md     # → 03-plan.md
│   │   └── ticket-writer-agent.md    # → tickets/T*.md
│   ├── execution/                    # Phase 2 — code implementation
│   │   ├── db-agent.md
│   │   ├── storage-agent.md
│   │   ├── api-agent.md
│   │   ├── auth-agent.md
│   │   ├── frontend-agent.md
│   │   ├── test-writer-agent.md      # Unit + integration tests
│   │   └── e2e-test-writer-agent.md
│   ├── testing/                      # Phase 3 — run tests, mutation testing
│   │   ├── test-runner-agent.md      # Runs full suite, self-heals E2E
│   │   └── mutation-tester-agent.md
│   └── validation/                   # Phase 4 — final review
│       └── reviewer-agent.md
├── skills/
│   ├── agent-registry.md
│   ├── database/                   # Hierarchical: _index.md + specific files
│   │   ├── _index.md               # Root: summary, routing table
│   │   ├── connection.md
│   │   ├── schema.md
│   │   ├── transactions.md
│   │   ├── error-handling.md
│   │   ├── queries.md
│   │   └── migrations.md
│   ├── auth/                      # Better Auth: _index, best-practices, security, 2FA, orgs
│   ├── supabase.md
│   ├── hono.md
│   ├── trpc.md
│   ├── react.md
│   ├── tanstack.md
│   ├── shadcn.md
│   └── typescript.md
├── rules/
│   ├── stack-context.mdc             # Always-on: tech stack, auth, testing
│   └── intent-routing.mdc            # Classify: full feature / continue / quick fix / review
├── hooks/
│   ├── cursor/
