│   │   ├── block-dangerous-commands.js
│   │   └── post-tool-use-check.js
│   └── git/
│       └── commit-msg-append-review.sh
├── commands/
│   └── commit.md
└── README
```

---

## 5-Phase Pipeline

| Phase | Directory | Agents | Output |
|-------|-----------|--------|--------|
| **0. Discovery** | `agents/discovery/` | requirements-agent, ux-designer-agent*, test-strategist-agent | 00-requirements.md, 01-ui-spec.md, 02-test-spec.md |
| **1. Planning** | `agents/planning/` | orchestrator-agent, ticket-writer-agent | 03-plan.md, tickets/T*.md |
| **2. Execution** | `agents/execution/` | test-writer-agent, e2e-test-writer-agent, db-agent, storage-agent, api-agent, auth-agent, frontend-agent | Code files |
| **3. Testing** | `agents/testing/` | test-runner-agent, mutation-tester-agent | Test results, fixes |
| **4. Validation** | `agents/validation/` | reviewer-agent | Review appended to plan, commit snippet |

*ux-designer-agent runs only when the feature has UI.

**Artifact flow:**

```
00-requirements.md  ← requirements-agent (discovery)
01-ui-spec.md      ← ux-designer-agent (discovery, conditional)
02-test-spec.md    ← test-strategist-agent (discovery)

         ↓ all 3 feed into

03-plan.md         ← orchestrator-agent (planning)

         ↓ plan feeds into

tickets/T01-*.md, T02-*.md, ...  ← ticket-writer-agent (planning)

         ↓ each ticket feeds its execution agent

         execution agents produce code

         ↓ then

test-runner-agent (testing)  → runs suite, fixes failures
mutation-tester-agent (testing)  → Stryker, kills survivors

         ↓ finally

reviewer-agent (validation)  → review, commit snippet
```

---

